{"tid":248252,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"D Mk以為有少少腹肌就好撚好打","createTime":"2017-05-18T12:01:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T16:20:39.000Z","uid":1777,"like":164,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f4bae15870461a161390eee7c0ef97ec62f42b67","tid":248252,"uid":1777,"like":28,"dislike":3,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T12:01:58.000Z","msg":"想當年我仲讀緊BAND 3中學<br />\n<br />\n有條MK撚狗咁撚我, 話約我隻揪<br />\n佢以為自己有腹肌就好撚好打<br />\n<br />\n(但其實我當時己經舉左兩三年鐵,一直有飲奶粉<br />\n不過我BULK緊, 即係夜神起義 Bane 果種大隻型<br />\n所以D肌肉線條未現到出黎)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我D 毒撚FD 嚇撚到標尿<br />\n「唔好同佢打呀, 佢有腹肌架」<br />\n「你痴左線咩, 你見唔見到佢幾咁FIT 呀」<br />\n<br />\n我心諗話你怕你嬲<br />\n有腹肌唔等於有力量<br />\n我笑笑口咁答應左條MK 放學去籃球場打過<br />\n<br />\nfast forward 去到決戰時間<br />\n成班同學企哂係側邊睇<br />\n佢就除左件校服<br />\n成個小丑咁係到谷佢果幾舊腹肌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到成班以為佢好好打果個情景,我真係快忍不住笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然最後佢打到我仆街, 牙都甩埋<br />\n但完全同腹肌冇關"},{"pid":"b678c67abfc8fd33e302aa01437331e6f9a18ca1","tid":248252,"uid":10845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T12:03:59.000Z","msg":"Old new is so 唔識串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"300dc56e29deeb8a33ceb065ea5cb13ab01d2180","tid":248252,"uid":90855,"like":0,"dislike":50,"score":-50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T12:08:24.000Z","msg":"曲線讚自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結論：樓主都係mk仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">MK仔食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"59a51fe0f9a3f